profile_info.description: My work, featuring popular originals ported from Yodayo and EFRO.AI, and new characters created exclusively on JanitorAI, is meticulously crafted to trap you in truly noxious scenarios:
profile_info.niche: Potent gassy girls, full-blown skunk characters, and overpowering stench scenarios.
profile_info.goal: From a shy girl's accidental flatulence to a full skunk spray dungeon crawl—prepare for total immersion.
profile_info.commitment: Every bot is crafted and tested over at least 5 hours for maximum quality and depth. I don't just create; I build communities: Founder of the legendary SkunkChatbots subreddit. Moderator for EFROChatbots.

featured_scenarios.name: Skunk Supremacy: Choose Your Fate
featured_scenarios.description: The world is under the pervasive, musky rule of Skunk Hybrids. Decide whether you are a Human Slave, forced into eternal servitude and olfactory torment, or a proud Skunk Hybrid Ruler, enjoying your gassy dominion.

featured_scenarios.name: Hotel Overbooking Chaos
featured_scenarios.description: Forced roommate duty with four Skunk-Human Hybrids! You're a low-priority human, kicked out of your room and now trapped in close quarters with Chloe, Lilly, Amy, and Lola. Prepare for mandatory compliance and immediate olfactory dominance in a world where their noxious, high-volume gas is the law.

featured_scenarios.name: The Twelve Days of Stenchmas
featured_scenarios.description: CHRISTMAS SCENARIO: A Naughty List fate where the human slave must survive twelve escalating stages of musky torture leading up to the final, unbearable Christmas Day punishment. (Focus: Endurance, Accumulation)

featured_scenarios.name: The Holiday Musk List
featured_scenarios.description: CHRISTMAS SCENARIO: You've made the Naughty List! Wrapped and sealed inside a sturdy gift box, you become the Hybrids' personal 'Fart Box.' The Skunk Girls take turns sitting atop the box, delivering concentrated gas through a specially prepared opening as punishment for your disobedience. (Focus: Forced Containment, Farting, Olfactory Torture)
